{"id":22361,"date":"2024-01-31T17:19:48","date_gmt":"2023-05-31T17:19:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=22361"},"modified":"2024-02-09T09:56:12","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T04:26:12","slug":"space-saving-sofa-bed","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/space-saving-sofa-bed\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Smart Space-Saving Sofa Bed Designs For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Comfortable seating and comfortable sleep: sofa beds are a win-win for your home<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With modern homes, especially in the post-pandemic period, it has become vital to have furniture and spaces that aid multiple uses. Sofa beds that seemed to have become a thing of the past have found their place in today\u2019s homes, big or small.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A space-saving sofa bed is a convenient piece of furniture to have in a studio apartment or a small apartment. In a spacious apartment, a sofa bed can come in handy in that extra room that you are currently using as a workspace, a recreation zone or a play area for the kids \u2014 the possibilities are endless. Take a look at these seven innovative sofa bed options for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Space-Saving Sofa Bed For A Small Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Trying to fit in all essential furniture in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">small bedroom<\/a> can be a real challenge. You definitely need a wardrobe for storage and a bed for a good night\u2019s sleep. Add to that a study or workstation, seating options and the space can get too cluttered. A sofa bed can give you free space during the day, additional seating, storage as well as a comfortable bed. This is a classic space-saving sofa bed design where you have to pull the other half of the unit to convert the sofa into a bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31164721\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving sofa bed which gives you an additional seating, storage as well as a comfortable bed\" class=\"wp-image-22383\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31164721\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31164721\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31164721\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31164721\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wondering how to fit in a bed full-time in a small bedroom? Get a sofa bed instead!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas\/\">small bedroom storage ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">One For A Cosy Corner<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a favourite nook in the house that you would like to convert into a cosy corner? A space-saving sofa bed would be just perfect. A perfect spot to have a cup of tea in the evening or to simply curl up with your favourite book, the sofa bed can also turn into an extra bed whenever you need it. The bright cushions and bed line make it look like the cheerful little nook that it is.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165123\/one-space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-cosy-corner.jpg\" alt=\"Space saving sofa bed for a cosy corner\" class=\"wp-image-22391\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165123\/one-space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-cosy-corner.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165123\/one-space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-cosy-corner-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165123\/one-space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-cosy-corner-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165123\/one-space-saving-sofa-bed-for-a-cosy-corner-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sofa bed is a right fit for a cosy corner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Space-Saving Sofa Bed To Lounge, Sleep, Repeat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/seating-ideas-for-home\/\">comfortable seating option<\/a> for your TV room? If you are torn between getting a sofa and getting a recliner, you can consider getting a sofa bed instead. Most of these modern design options consist of units that can be moved around and rearranged at your convenience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165322\/space-saving-sofa-bed-to-lounge-sleep-repeat.jpg\" alt=\"Grey space-saving sofa bed to lounger sleep and repeat with the tv\" class=\"wp-image-22392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165322\/space-saving-sofa-bed-to-lounge-sleep-repeat.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165322\/space-saving-sofa-bed-to-lounge-sleep-repeat-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165322\/space-saving-sofa-bed-to-lounge-sleep-repeat-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165322\/space-saving-sofa-bed-to-lounge-sleep-repeat-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sofa bed can be a good idea for your TV room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sofa Bed Heaven<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This sofa bed design has made it to the list more because of the utter comfort and style that it offers. Also, a reminder that sofa beds need not necessarily be for smaller spaces only. They can add glamour to a spacious lounging space in your home too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165533\/space-saving-sofa-bed-heaven.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving sofa bed in pure-white colour\" class=\"wp-image-22394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165533\/space-saving-sofa-bed-heaven.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165533\/space-saving-sofa-bed-heaven-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165533\/space-saving-sofa-bed-heaven-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165533\/space-saving-sofa-bed-heaven-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Not all sofa beds are for small spaces<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sofa Bed To Provide Extra Seating In The Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A spacious <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/trendy-living-room-seating-ideas\/\">seating arrangement for your living room<\/a> that can also be reassembled into a comfortable bed for unplanned stayovers, this sofa bed can be a great addition to your living room. Another way this can be useful is to change the seating arrangement from time to time \u2014 every time you feel like giving your space a spruce-up.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165805\/space-saving-sofa-to-provide-extra-seating-in-the-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving sofa bed to provide extra seating in the living room\" class=\"wp-image-22396\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165805\/space-saving-sofa-to-provide-extra-seating-in-the-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165805\/space-saving-sofa-to-provide-extra-seating-in-the-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165805\/space-saving-sofa-to-provide-extra-seating-in-the-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165805\/space-saving-sofa-to-provide-extra-seating-in-the-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A free-to-reassemble sofa can be a better option than a fixed design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multipurpose Sofa Bed For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Does a love seat seem like a good option for your studio space, but you could do with an additional seating option? A small space-saving sofa bed can help you achieve both. An extra movable seat can practically fit into any space, and the convertible bed can come in handy if you are splitting a studio space with a roommate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165942\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-small-spaces.jpg\" alt=\"Small space-saving sofa bed in blue colour\" class=\"wp-image-22397\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165942\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-small-spaces.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165942\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-small-spaces-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165942\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-small-spaces-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31165942\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-small-spaces-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sofa beds are blessings for studio apartment owners<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sofa Bed For The Balcony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A balcony or a terrace in your apartment can easily be the place where you unwind from time to time. Standard furniture options like chairs and a table are always good, but a sofa bed can be a more comfortable option here and a space-saving one at that. We can already picture ourselves having some time off with our favourite read here!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31170116\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-the-balcony.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving sofa bed for the balcony\" class=\"wp-image-22398\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31170116\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-the-balcony.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31170116\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-the-balcony-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31170116\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-the-balcony-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/31170116\/space-saving-sofa-bed-for-the-balcony-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Looking for an option to garden furniture for a balcony? A sofa bed can serve the purpose<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the things that you should consider while choosing the right space-saving sofa bed for your home are: <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Style: <\/strong>Do you want a sofa that can be extended into a bed or a rearrangeable piece?<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Storage: <\/strong>The old-school sofa beds come with storage facilities if that\u2019s a must-have for you.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fabric And Mattress\/Cushions: <\/strong>When you are practically planning to use it as a sofa and a bed, the material and mattress should be such that it makes the sofa bed comfortable in both forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a favourite space-saving sofa bed pick? Tell us about it in the comments!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about space saving sofa bed designs, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/sofa-colour-combination\/\">sofa colour combinations.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our design experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"f